    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been super reliable for me and is still in really solid shape! It's got that 'well-loved' feel\u2014not brand new, but it runs like a dream and has plenty of life left in it. Perfect for someone who needs a dependable daily driver without the 'off-the-lot' price tag. I\u2019ve taken great care of it, and I'm sure you'll love driving it as much as I have. Come check it out and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8. This high-revving powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a cross-plane crank to deliver linear power up to an 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut with a functional M-Variable Differential Lock and EDC-equipped suspension providing precise lateral grip. While showing minor aesthetic patina consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain is robust, with recent rod bearing service and throttle actuator replacements completed. A driver-focused example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean title. Regularly serviced. Reliable daily driver. Minimal wear.",
