    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a fantastic blend of reliability and comfort. The exterior finish remains vibrant, showing only the minor, expected signs of careful road use. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean; the seats are supportive and free of significant wear, and all interior electronics\u2014including the premium sound system and navigation\u2014are fully operational. Under the hood, the car has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer\u2019s schedule, with a recent multi-point inspection and fluid top-off already completed. The tires provide excellent grip, and the brakes feel firm and responsive. It delivers a smooth, quiet ride that testament to its consistent upkeep. This is a turn-key vehicle perfect for anyone seeking a dependable daily driver that has been treated with respect.",
      "price": 34500.0,
